<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>We are building a team to respond to ICE activity in the West MI Indivisible area. Attendees will learn a brief history of ICE and its local context, be trained on how to provide emergency and ongoing support to families affected by ICE, and safely patrol and document ICE presence.  Please register with your full name.  You must bring a photo ID with you to check in to the training. You will receive an email 24 hours in advance of the training with specific location details. 

