        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>No Kings III</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Saturday, March 28, 2026 at 5:00 PM UTC - 7:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Curwood Castle Drive<br>Curwood Castle Dr<br>Owosso, MI 48867</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Shiawassee County Democratic Party</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>No Kings III: The Shiawassee County Democratic Party is organizing a third No Kings rally and protest in solidarity with other community members and groups to voice concerns about ICE, reduction in services for vulnerable citizens and protection of voting rights. Our country is not run by a king. We uphold our local, state and national values, interests and laws to support our Democracy. Meet at Curwood Castle for a short presentation and walk together in solidarity with Peaceful Protest to the M21 Bridge across from and in front of the Owosso City Hall.</p>
