        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>ICE Out of OC: CLEMIS Authority Executive Meeting</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Thursday, February 26, 2026 at 3:00 PM UTC - 5:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>𝐖𝐡𝐢𝐭𝐞 𝐋𝐚𝐤𝐞 𝐂𝐡𝐚𝐫𝐭𝐞𝐫 𝐓𝐨𝐰𝐧𝐬𝐡𝐢𝐩 𝐇𝐚𝐥𝐥<br>7525 Highland Road<br>White Lake, MI 48383</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> NE Oakland Indivisible</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>### 𝐏𝐮𝐛𝐥𝐢𝐜 𝐌𝐞𝐞𝐭𝐢𝐧𝐠: 𝐂𝐋𝐄𝐌𝐈𝐒 &amp; 𝐈𝐂𝐄 — 𝐋𝐞𝐭’𝐬 𝐇𝐨𝐥𝐝 𝐓𝐡𝐞𝐦 𝐀𝐜𝐜𝐨𝐮𝐧𝐭𝐚𝐛𝐥𝐞

## NEW LOCATION

### The meeting location has changed — and we need people engaged.

Toolkit:  https://rb.gy/2m13zp (CLEMIS email templates &amp; SM assets)

County leaders have said they support ending the CLEMIS contract with ICE. The contract expires 𝐌𝐚𝐫𝐜𝐡 𝟑𝟏. Now we make sure it is 𝐧𝐨𝐭 𝐫𝐞𝐧𝐞𝐰𝐞𝐝.

🗓 𝐓𝐡𝐮𝐫𝐬𝐝𝐚𝐲, 𝐅𝐞𝐛 𝟐𝟔

⏰ 𝟏𝟎:𝟎𝟎 𝐀𝐌

📍 𝐖𝐡𝐢𝐭𝐞 𝐋𝐚𝐤𝐞 𝐂𝐡𝐚𝐫𝐭𝐞𝐫 𝐓𝐨𝐰𝐧𝐬𝐡𝐢𝐩 𝐇𝐚𝐥𝐥

7525 Highland Road

White Lake, MI 48383

👥 Open to the public

✅ 𝐒𝐡𝐨𝐰 𝐮𝐩

✅ 𝐄𝐦𝐚𝐢𝐥 𝐂𝐋𝐄𝐌𝐈𝐒 (contact here: https://shorturl.at/ZbUZG )

✅ 𝐑𝐞𝐬𝐡𝐚𝐫𝐞 𝐭𝐡𝐢𝐬 𝐩𝐨𝐬𝐭

No renewal.

No new contracts.

Let’s hold them accountable.

More about CLEMIS [here](https://www.govtech.com/public-safety/clemis-police-and-court-database-plans-national-growth).</p>
<p><a href="https://www.mobilize.us/event/908663/" target="_blank">View Event on Mobilize.us</a></p>
<p><i>Data source: mobilize.us | Updated: 2026-02-25T07:04:10.471Z</i></p>
]]></description>
