        <name>No Kings 3 (Traverse City)</name>
        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>No Kings 3 (Traverse City)</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Saturday, March 28, 2026 at 5:00 PM UTC - 7:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Traverse City<br><br>Traverse City, MI 49684</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Traverse Indivisible</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>SAVE THE DATE: No Kings 3 is Coming to Traverse City!

Saturday, March 28 | 1:00 PM - 3:00 PM | Traverse City, Michigan

Democracy is under assault. ICE raids are terrorizing our neighborhoods. Our national debt has hit 100% of GDP while authoritarianism tightens its grip. We&apos;re not backing down, we&apos;re turning up the volume!

No Kings 3 will be our biggest, loudest protest yet, and we need YOU there.

Why register now?
Even without full details finalized, your early registration helps us with critical event logistics and crowd estimates. We&apos;re building something powerful, and every name counts.

What we know so far:
✊ This will be a joyful AND loud event
🎵 Bring your signs, your singing voice, noisemakers, and ALL your energy
📢 We&apos;re making noise for democracy

Looking to get involved?
Email membership@traverseindivisible.org to find out about our much needed volunteer opportunities.

What&apos;s coming:
We&apos;ll update this page with specifics on format, exact location, and ADA accessibility as soon as they&apos;re finalized. Stay tuned!

Spread the word!
Share this event far and wide. Text your friends. Post on social media. We need maximum turnout to send a clear message: We will not be silent. We will not bow down.

No Kings. No Tyrants. No Backing Down.

See you March 28th! 🗽

---

A core principle behind all Traverse Indivisible events is a commitment to nonviolent action and peaceful resistance. We expect all participants to seek to de-escalate any potential confrontation with those who disagree with our values, and to act lawfully at these events. Weapons of any kind, including those legally permitted, should not be brought to events.</p>
<p><a href="https://www.mobilize.us/event/898910/" target="_blank">View Event on Mobilize.us</a></p>
<p><i>Data source: mobilize.us | Updated: 2026-02-25T07:04:10.471Z</i></p>
]]></description>
