    <Placemark>
        <name>We the People Dissent Bi-Monthly Grand Circus Protest THEMED: ART AGAINST ICE</name>
        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>We the People Dissent Bi-Monthly Grand Circus Protest THEMED: ART AGAINST ICE</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Sunday, March 1, 2026 at 6:00 PM UTC - 7:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Grand Circus Park<br><br>Détroit, MI 48226</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Indivisible</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>THEME: ART AGAINST ICE

Compose your own poem, bring a poem from an author who honored the memory of a victim of ICE, or come with a song that you want to share and have people sing with you.

Join us for an hour of action at Grand Circus Park in Downtown Detroit. Let&apos;s give the resistance in Detroit some good visibility, educate people about the democratic crisis we are deep in with flyering and conversations. We have banners, but feel free to bring your best sign! Make sure you come with water and a snack in your backpack, warm gloves, layers of sweaters under your winter coat, long johns, scarf, and winter hat. Heated socks sound like a good idea too.

At 1PM, we will start at the corner of Adams &amp; Woodward, just next to Central Methodist Church. We may decide to move to a different corner depending on where the crowd flows, but the meeting point at 1 PM is just outside the Church!

On Sundays, street parking is free. You can also park in the church parking lot. Mention at the gate that you are here for the protest. If you cannot find street parking available near Grand Circus, we recommend that you drive up Woodward a bit, where you can park anywhere for free, then hop on the Q-Line (free too!) to Grand Circus. 

*A core principle behind all Indivisible events is a commitment to nonviolent action. We expect all participants to seek to de-escalate any potential confrontation with those who disagree with our values.*</p>
<p><a href="https://www.mobilize.us/event/873812/" target="_blank">View Event on Mobilize.us</a></p>
<p><i>Data source: mobilize.us | Updated: 2026-02-25T07:04:10.471Z</i></p>
]]></description>
