        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>ICE Out Poetry Event</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Sunday, March 1, 2026 at 3:00 PM UTC - 5:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Radical Bean Cooperative<br>123 E McMicken Ave<br>Cincinnati, OH 45202</p>
