<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>About Face Cincinnati and NKY Against ICE are cosponsoring a poetry event, featuring local poets Lucky Lee and Mo Viviane! They will share their poetry, and in-between we will hear from the work folks are doing to help protect our communities. 

