    <Placemark>
        <name>Kenton County Fiscal Court (Covington) - Oppose ICE in our Communities</name>
        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>Kenton County Fiscal Court (Covington) - Oppose ICE in our Communities</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Tuesday, March 24, 2026 at 9:30 PM UTC - 11:30 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Kenton County Fiscal Court<br>1840 Simon Kenton Wy<br>Covington, KY 41011</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Kentuckians For The Commonwealth</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>People are gathering at the Kenton County Fiscal Court to speak during public comment on the fact that Kenton County has 287-g agreement, allowing for the county police to do immigration enforcement.

While the decision may ultimately be up to the Sheriff, this is the chance to tell all of our elected officials that we oppose ICE operating in our community, using our local police to do their work, and want to make sure that all of our neighbors feel safe.</p>
