        <name>Four Corners Rally for Justice</name>
        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>Four Corners Rally for Justice</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Saturday, February 28, 2026 at 6:00 PM UTC - 7:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Marita Park behind RCU parking lot, across from Dick&apos;s Market<br>Minnesota Ave<br>New Richmond, WI 54017</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Indivisible</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>This a local Indivisible event!

We need to SHINE A LIGHT on the many INJUSTICES that this regime is putting upon us - expanded detention polices with no due process, Redistricting= gerrymandering=voter suppression, limits on gender-affirming care for minors, limits on access to reproductive healthcare, rolling back environmental regulations, governing via executive order vs legislation, expanded ICE with no accountability. You get the idea. Dress for the weather, bring friends and signs. We know it will be cold again this week, showing up is the most important thing we can do to make our voices heard. And it&apos;s one hour! Let&apos;s fill all four corners, HWY 65 and Business 64, by Dick&apos;s Market!

*A core principle behind all Indivisible events is a commitment to nonviolent action. We expect all participants to seek to de-escalate any potential confrontation with those who disagree with our values.*</p>
