<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>7400 Metro Blvd<br>Edina, MN 55439</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Indivisible MN03</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Afflict the comfortable! And the Minnesota GOP is too comfortable with the violence and chaos that ICE has brought to our cities.

