        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>Coffee and Conversation: Chaska</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Wednesday, March 11, 2026 at 7:00 PM UTC - 9:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Jones Coffee (Chaska)<br>100 E 2nd St<br>Chaska, MN 55318</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Minnesota DFL</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Join your Carver County Community Organizer, Sam, for this lowkey event at Jones Coffee in Chaska with a focus on building community during these turbulent times. Got a news article you want to share? Want to chat about ways that we can make a difference in 2026? Want to ask Sam what his favorite flavor of ice cream is? (it&apos;s mint chocolate chip). Come grab some coffee, tea, or a pastry and support a great local business in the company of like-minded neighbors. Feel free to join for the whole time or just stop in for a few minutes!</p>
