        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>Plymouth Monday Weekly Protest</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Monday, March 2, 2026 at 10:00 PM UTC - 11:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>2700 Annapolis Cir N<br>Plymouth, MN 55441</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Indivisible West Metro</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Come out and support the community by showing we are not afraid of ICE and this administration!

Invite your friends, family or coworkers; bring a sign, a flag, whatever you&apos;re interested in holding.

Please make sure to stay on the sidewalk as people do drive fast on 55 and when entering 55.

There is parking by the Caribou or the Holiday. Arrive when you are able; leave when when you need to.

All local protests organized by Indivisible MN03 are peaceful, legal, nonviolent, family-friendly exercises of first amendment rights in public places.</p>
