<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>William S. Moorhead Federal Building<br>1000 Liberty Ave<br>Pittsburgh, PA 15222</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Indivisible Pittsburgh</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Mondays With(out) McCormick is now Fridays With(out) Fetterman!

