    <Placemark>
        <name>National Day of Lobbying 2: Impeach, Convict, Remove - Kansas City, MO (MO-06)</name>
        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>National Day of Lobbying 2: Impeach, Convict, Remove - Kansas City, MO (MO-06)</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Monday, March 9, 2026 at 9:00 PM UTC - 10:30 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Rep. Sam Graves&apos; Kansas City Office<br>12200 N Ambassador Dr Ste 234<br>Kansas City, MO 64163</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> 50501Missouri</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Democracy does not defend itself; it requires the active participation of the people. This moment demands something very visible, direct, and powerful: constituents showing up at congressional district offices, where staff rarely, if ever, engage with constituents.

On 2.17, constituents from across all 50 states went into at least 110 in-district offices of US Representatives to talk about impeaching Trump and abolishing ICE. Some offices locked their doors and appeared visibly shaken (e.g., Eric Burlison, Mo US 7th District); others sat down and had tough conversations with constituents. Across most offices – a common theme emerged: we don’t want to have to see you and have this discussion again.

So, on 3.9 – we’re going back! Impeachment is not optional. It is the remedy mandated by the Constitution. Likewise, Congress holds the power to de-fund and abolish ICE. They aren’t acting because they do not have the political will to do so. So we will lend them some more of ours. 

On Monday, 3/9, FLARE USA, Citizens&apos; Impeachment, Sons of Liberty, state chapters of 50501, progressive candidates, and many other concerned citizens will join together in leading constituents into the local/in-district offices of all 435 US House Representatives to demand impeachment and the abolishment of ICE.

WHERE:  Sam Graves, US 6th District Representative&apos;s Kansas City Office - 12200 N Ambassador Drive, KCMO.  We will be on the public sidewalk along Ambassador Drive.  4-5:30 pm.  If you are unable to physically attend, take a moment to call and ask Sam Graves to impeach Trump and abolish ICE.

Make sure to join the Impeachment Coalition for additional messaging and to connect with other organizers. You can join here: https://citizensimpeachment.com/the-impeachment-coalition/

All actions under this banner are committed to lawful, non-violent action and no civil disobedience. 

By registering for the event, you are agreeing that event partners may receive your contact information and communicate with you about related activities.</p>
<p><a href="https://www.mobilize.us/event/910667/" target="_blank">View Event on Mobilize.us</a></p>
<p><i>Data source: mobilize.us | Updated: 2026-02-25T07:04:10.471Z</i></p>
]]></description>
