<h3>End the ICE Age</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Friday, March 6, 2026 at 9:00 PM UTC - 10:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>I-99 Overpass at Toftrees Exit<br>Waddle Road &amp; Colonnade Boulevard<br>Patton Township, PA 16803</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Keystone Indivisible</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>We are looking to thaw ICE!  Join us for an overpass protest this Friday.  Treat the incoming wrestling fans to messages about the excesses of ICE.

Located at the I-99 Overpass at Toftrees exit (near Waddle Road &amp; Colonnade Boulevard). Parking is behind nearby Sheetz and NOT BEHIND Cracker Barrel.

Overpass and bridge traffic messages will relate to the cruelty of ICE. If you have a sign related to this message please bring it; we will bring signs that can be held also. Waddle Road bridge traffic messages (upper) are as important as the I-99 incoming traffic messages (lower). The overpass can be windy -- be sure to dress warmly. Stay for however long works for you; be mindful of your health!</p>
<p><a href="https://www.mobilize.us/event/900019/" target="_blank">View Event on Mobilize.us</a></p>
<p><i>Data source: mobilize.us | Updated: 2026-02-25T07:04:10.471Z</i></p>
