        <name>Signs of Justice Postcard Party</name>
        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>Signs of Justice Postcard Party</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Thursday, February 26, 2026 at 8:00 PM UTC - 9:30 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Creekside Provisions + Supplies<br>123 Congress St<br>Berkeley Springs, WV 25411</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Indivisible</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>This a local Indivisible event!

We will be gathering at a local business to write 100 postcards to our Members of Congress. We are joining the Signs of Justice 12 MILLION POSTCARDS Campaign “We the People Oppose Unchecked Federal polICE power.”(https://www.signsofjustice.com/products/we-the-people)

NO TROOPS in cities without state approval. NO ICE RAIDS without a judicial warrant. DUE PROCESS for ALL including non-citizens.
The Constitution is clear: Article VI and Amendments 4,5, &amp; 14. 

The majority of Americans agree on these issues. Congress needs to hear this again &amp; again, so let&apos;s Flood Congress with the FACTS!

We’ll provide the printed postcards, the pens &amp; markers, and the stamps. All of us will be writing additional messages on the cards &amp; addressing them. They will be mailed in bulk on March 1st.

Have questions? mcwvindivisible@gmail.com

*A core principle behind all Indivisible events is a commitment to nonviolent action. We expect all participants to seek to de-escalate any potential confrontation with those who disagree with our values.*</p>
