        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>Know Your Rights &amp; Community Organizing Event</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Saturday, February 28, 2026 at 6:30 PM UTC - 9:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Neighborhood Church<br>1561 McLendon Ave NE<br>Atlanta, GA 30307</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> 50501 Georgia</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Please join us from 1:30-4 p.m. at Neighborhood Church in Candler Park (1561 McClendon Ave) to come together with Candler Park and Lake Claire neighbors who are concerned about the presence of ICE in our neighborhoods. This is an opportunity for us to share our stories, connect with resources, and organize. 

We will join together in the spirit of resilience and building community. This event will include

1. Know Your Rights Training and Resources
2. Initiatives and ways that you can get involved right now
