        <name>Pack the MPD Oversight Hearing</name>
        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>Pack the MPD Oversight Hearing</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Wednesday, February 25, 2026 at 2:00 PM UTC - 9:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>The John Wilson Building<br>1350 Pennsylvania Ave NW<br>Washington, DC 20004</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Harriet’s Wildest Dreams</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>DC Elected officials continue to leave their power on the table, if they won&apos;t do anything, the people will. On February 25th, we are asking DC residents to show up and pack the MPD Performance Oversight Hearing. Performance oversight hearings are annual reviews of agencies in the DC government. 

As the public we have to demand that our elected officials and agencies DO NOT COOPERATE WITH THE OCCUPATION OF OUR CITY. We demand ICE OUT, the National Guard off our streets and MPD end all collaboration with federal agencies that terrorize our communities. 

We need you to testify before council, pack the hearing room, conduct walk around and office visits. Show up and take up space, the Wilson Building is the people&apos;s building and we have a right to be there.</p>
<p><a href="https://www.mobilize.us/event/892206/" target="_blank">View Event on Mobilize.us</a></p>
