<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>This a local Indivisible event sponsored by Southern Crescent Indivisible of Georgia.

This event is a street protest. Protesters with a variety of signs and flags line up along the sidewalk of a busy street. We wave at drivers, smile at the supportive honks, and talk with fellow protesters.

You can bring your own sign (no profanity, please) or borrow one of ours. 

