        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>ICE Out For Good: week of calls</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Wednesday, February 25, 2026 at 5:00 AM UTC - 5:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Location not specified</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Indivisible</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>## Rein in ICE for Good: Week of Calls/Email Campaign

### Week of February 23 – March 1, 2026**

**Suggested topics: Check out [5calls.org](5calls.org) for in depth scripts, if preferred.**

- **State Specific Action**: Ask your Governor and State representatives to oppose ICE using department of [motor vehicle data for tracking.](https://5calls.org/issue/ice-dmv-data-flock-surveillance/)
 
- Impeach Pam Bondi
- Oppose the SAVE America Act Senate Specific (Call script here: https://indivisible.org/actions/stop-save-senate/)
- Repeal DHS funding from HR1 OBBBA
- Demand federal agents unmask and use body cameras when doing federal law enforcement.
- Impeach Kristi Noem 
- Demand Stephen Miller Resignation
 
Hi, my name is **[NAME]** and I’m a constituent from **[CITY, ZIP]**. (Leave full address if leaving a voicemail).

I’m calling to urge **[REP/SEN NAME]* to **[Insert Topic]*. [Include personal relevance or topic specific data here].  

Thank you for your time and consideration.

*A core principle behind all Indivisible events is a commitment to nonviolent action. We expect all participants to seek to de-escalate any potential confrontation with those who disagree with our values.*</p>
