        <name>NEPA Stands Up Troublemakers Cafe: Mix, Mingle, Organize! Social Hour</name>
        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>NEPA Stands Up Troublemakers Cafe: Mix, Mingle, Organize! Social Hour</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Saturday, February 28, 2026 at 8:00 PM UTC - 10:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>The Spare Oom Tattoo<br>2239 Pittston Ave<br>Scranton, PA 18505</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Pennsylvania Stands Up</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>A casual community building space to plug into our working groups and campaigns. Get to know NEPA Stands Up! Join us at The Spare Oom Tattoo in Scranton for crafts, board games, conversation, and snacks from 3pm-5pm! We welcome folks to bring their favorite cozy activities and goodies for the group to share. 

At NEPA Stands Up we&apos;re working to build a political home for poor and working folks across race, place, and generation who are fed up with billionaires and bought politicians fixing the system in their favor while the rest of us struggle to get by. We know that we the people have the power and it&apos;s up to us to come together to demand better as a community. Whether that means taking on data centers that rise our utility rates and waste our precious resources, pressuring our elected officials to fight for our constitutional rights and community safety by stopping funding and collaboration with ICE, or working with allies to affirm and codify the right of LGBTQIA+ youth to get a safe and equal education, we know that it&apos;s up to us to save us. 

Our monthly Troublemakers Cafe is a space for folks to gather in community, build solidarity, and learn from each other on a variety of topics.</p>
<p><a href="https://www.mobilize.us/event/909400/" target="_blank">View Event on Mobilize.us</a></p>
<p><i>Data source: mobilize.us | Updated: 2026-02-25T07:04:10.471Z</i></p>
]]></description>
