<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>SPEAK OUT NOW peaceful protests continue! We will gather on the first and third Saturdays of each month to protest the cruelty of the ice raids and all of the unconstitutional and corrupt practices of this administration. What is happening in our country is not normal, the world is watching, and we must continue making our voices heard!
