<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Indivisible One New Jersey (IONJ)</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>WCATNJ MONTHLY MEETING WITH DR. BETH ADUBATO AND BRIAN VARELA

Come join our in person meeting and be part of the discussion for the direction of 2026!  Meet Dr. Beth Adubato and *Brian Varela, CD7 candidates asking for your vote.  Your voice matters in Warren County! 

 Find out about our strategies to engage voters, make candidates accountable, our Visibility Brigade, Finding Kean Washington Bor., Purple light campaign, post carding, meet and greet candidates, canvassing and more. If you wondered if you are the only one, come see that you are not! It&apos;s a great opportunity to connect with our like minded community and get involved a little or a lot.💜 

The meeting will be in person and virtual via Zoom. The location and Zoom link will be emailed to you prior to the meeting.  Members, we will be meeting in our normal location,  please see Slack and or Facebook.

To join our WC Visibility Brigade please email us at wcatnj@gmail.com.  NO KINGS IS COMING MARCH 28, ARE YOU READY?! PHILLIPSBURG AND HACKETTSTOWN.  https://www.mobilize.us/ionj/event/894053/

