<h3>No Kings Sign Making Party</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Saturday, March 21, 2026 at 5:00 PM UTC - 7:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>1302 W Market St<br>Smithfield, NC 27577</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Indivisible Johnston County NC</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>This is a fun way to meet new people and get ready for No Kings.  You can make signs for yourself and others.  Bring supplies if you can. 
 
If you aren’t feeling artsy, come and pack whistle bags for ICE watchers.  We hope to pack 200 bags to be distributed at No Kings, so we need lots of help! Lunch will be provided but bring a drink.</p>
