<h3>Defrosting ICE Together</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Saturday, March 7, 2026 at 5:30 PM UTC - 8:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Bloomfield Avenue &amp; Lakeside Avenue<br>Verona, NJ 07044</p>
