        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>We Get Out the Resistance: One Million Rising</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Saturday, March 7, 2026 at 4:00 PM UTC - 5:30 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Albany Public Library<br>161 Washington Ave<br>Albany, NY 12210</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Indivisible</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>This event is hosted by We Get Out the Resistance, a Capital Region Indivisible Chapter and a member of the Greater Capital Region Coalition. 

Our PowerPoint, One Million RISING: A Call to Action outlines resisting the Trump Regime,  keeping our neighbors safe from ICE, supporting Democrats to win the 2026 mid-term elections and more. We will write postcards highlighting Trump&apos;s tariff ridden failed economy.

Light refreshments served. Please join us. No one can sit this one out!

*A core principle behind all Indivisible events is a commitment to nonviolent action. We expect all participants to seek to de-escalate any potential confrontation with those who disagree with our values.*</p>
