        <name>Small Business ICE Preparation Training</name>
        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>Small Business ICE Preparation Training</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Sunday, March 1, 2026 at 7:00 PM UTC - 8:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>City Tabernacle of Seventh-day Adventists<br>562 W 150th St<br>New York, NY 10031</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Indivisible Harlem</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>We invite Hamilton Heights small business owners, managers, and employees to join us to learn what to do now to protect yourselves if ICE tries to enter your business. 

We will cover what ICE can and cannot do, how to safely record, and share lots of additional resources for businesses. We&apos;ll provide free posters and signs to use in your business. We will also provide multilingual materials for you to share with your staff.</p>
<p><a href="https://www.mobilize.us/event/905557/" target="_blank">View Event on Mobilize.us</a></p>
