        <name>Rally To Defend Our Democracy with Jersey Shore Blue</name>
        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>Rally To Defend Our Democracy with Jersey Shore Blue</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Saturday, February 28, 2026 at 4:00 PM UTC - 5:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>269 NJ-35<br>Eatontown, NJ 07724</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Indivisible</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>This a local Indivisible event!

(These rallies were previously titled &quot;Musk or Us&quot;. Now we&apos;re showing up to highlight all our reasons to be outraged at the Trump administration.)

Under Trump and GOP leadership-

*millions have lost healthcare
*taxes are rising 
*everyday costs are soaring
*our streets are being militarized
*people are being disappeared
*pedophiles are shielded from accountability. 

Now, ICE is shooting people in the streets.

Trump’s administration is in full-blown power grab mode—shredding laws, defying court orders, and handing control of the country’s financial system to billionaire cronies.

We must apply relentless, all-out pressure to stop this coup in its tracks!

Bring your signs and raise your voice to highlight the issues you care most about.

Note-for your safety, please stay on the sidewalk. 📍 Where: [Tesla Dealership, Route 35, Eatontown, NJ] , 11:00 am-12:00 pm]

Sign up now and bring a friend!

*A core principle behind all Indivisible events is a commitment to nonviolent action. We expect all participants to seek to de-escalate any potential confrontation with those who disagree with our values.*</p>
