        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>Queens Afternoon of Craftivism</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Saturday, February 28, 2026 at 6:00 PM UTC - 9:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>214-25 42nd Ave<br>Queens, NY 11361</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Northeast Queens Indivisible</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>We have closed online reservations and are beginning a waitlist in order to make sure everyone has room to make their art.  Please email neqindivisible@gmail.com to be put on the waitlist and use CRAFTIVISM WAITLIST in the subject line!  Calling all Eastern Queens and Western Nassau Residents!  Join us for an afternoon of CRAFTIVISM in preparation for NO KINGS 3. Our community will create poster art and or share in a knitting/crocheting circle to make Melt the Ice Hats.  This great combo of creativity will provide the opportunity to share stories and ideas.  Please bring your own supplies for either action.  If you are inclined to knit or crochet you should refer to https://payhip.com/shopneedleandskein for details on material needed. 
For additional questions contact us at neqindivisible@gmail.com</p>
