<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>WE MUST STAND TOGETHER AND KEEP RESISTING IN 2026! Bring your energy and your signs, non-violent and PG-13 PLEASE,  and join the Northwest Resistance in speaking out &amp; standing up against this authoritarian regime! Every 2nd &amp; 4th Saturday through winter, on the Litchfield Town Green.  11am - 12pm

