<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Join us as we take our visibility brigade to the streets in our stand against ICE brutality! We will meet, decorate our cars with supplies we provide (feel free to bring extra removable chalk markers to write on your windows) and then head out. We will take a peaceful drive through Riverhead , showing our neighbors we want ICE Out. We suggest all drivers have at least one passenger to accompany them in order to film or wave from the passenger seats. NOTE: we will obey all traffic laws and posted speed limits.</p>
