        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>CITIZENS BANK - STOP FUNDING ICE PRISONS!!  WESTERLY 11am-Noon SAT MARCH 7th</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Saturday, March 7, 2026 at 4:00 PM UTC - 5:00 PM</p>
