<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> South County Rising RI</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Are you horrified by ICE?

Join South County Rising on Saturday, March 7th, 2026 from 11am -12pm as we stand out at Citizens Bank branch at 112 Franklin St in Westerly, RI to demand that they stop financing ICE prisons.

WE WILL HAVE OUR OVERPASS LETTERS SPELLING OUT ***ICE IS GESTAPO*** for folks to hold up.  And the Hotline #

