        <name>Indivisible LAB Daytime Action Hours</name>
        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>Indivisible LAB Daytime Action Hours</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Tuesday, March 10, 2026 at 2:30 PM UTC - 4:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Lexington Center (RSVP for details)<br><br>Lexington, MA 02421</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Indivisible LAB</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Join us for our Daytime Action Hours in Lexington Center. We&apos;ll have actions you can take during the meeting and information on events and actions planned this winter. Bring your ideas for actions and suggestions for future meetings.

Please RSVP to get location details and parking information.

Note: Our daytime meetings are now on Tuesdays since many members attend the Wednesday and Thursday 11am -1pm ICE protests in Burlington.</p>
