        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>Citizens Bank: Stop Financing ICE Prisons (Arlington Center)</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Saturday, March 7, 2026 at 4:00 PM UTC - 5:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br><br>Arlington, MA 02420</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Indivisible LAB</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Protests began on January 24 with more than 40 standouts and 1000 people at Citizens Banks across the Northeast. Keep the pressure on! Join our standout on March 7!

Citizens Bank claims it&apos;s dedicated to fostering strong communities. Yet it provides hundreds of millions of dollars in financial support and services to the country’s large for-profit prison and detention center builders and operators—CoreCivic and The GEO Group. While other US banks have pulled out of the business, Citizens Bank has deepened its ties with the big winners in ICE’s war on immigrants.

Customers and non-customers alike! Help let people know about Citizens Bank’s involvement with ICE. Sign up and join the protest sponsored by the De-ICE Citizens Bank Coalition on Saturday, January 24th 11am. Address available upon registration.  

Specific location available upon registration.

If you choose to, bring a sign with a message such as 
Citizens Banks: Stop Financing ICE Prisons!
Citizens Bank: Get Out of ICE Business!

We’ll have signs and handouts available.  Rain date January 31.

For more information about Citizens Bank’s relationship to the private prison system, go to [boycottcitizens.org](https://www.boycottcitizens.org/) or contact the De-ICE Citizens Bank Coalition of activist organizations in Massachusetts, Rhode Island, and beyond at de.ICE.CitizensBank@gmail.com.

*An interactive map of participating locations is available [here](https://www.google.com/maps/d/u/0/viewer?mid=1AqRhnn9dpUufZYdnkwFm6cDhqDWM6Tc&amp;ll=42.47280688951886%2C-71.8565222&amp;z=9).*</p>
<p><a href="https://www.mobilize.us/event/899183/" target="_blank">View Event on Mobilize.us</a></p>
<p><i>Data source: mobilize.us | Updated: 2026-02-25T07:04:10.471Z</i></p>
]]></description>
