        <name>De-Ice Citizen&apos;s Bank</name>
        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>De-Ice Citizen&apos;s Bank</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Saturday, March 7, 2026 at 4:00 PM UTC - 5:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>212 Elm St<br>Somerville, MA 02144</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> mystic mashup Indivisible</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Citizen&apos;s Bank finances ICE prisons! Join us- and be part of national protest - in a Stand Out outside Citizen&apos;s Bank in Somerville, MA, to protest the fact that Citizen&apos;s Bank is a primary funder of two for-profit prison companies that build and maintain detention facilities for ICE and provide transportation of ICE detainees.
These corportations - GEO Group and Core Civic - have been paid more than $11 BILLION by ICE over the last 10 years.  
Citizen&apos;s Bank bills itself as a community bank but this is not what we want in our community! Almost all other major US banks have gotten out of the business of funding these prison companies.
This is part of a national protest. Over 40 other sites will be protesting outside Citizen&apos;s Banks across the country on March 7.</p>
<p><a href="https://www.mobilize.us/event/910791/" target="_blank">View Event on Mobilize.us</a></p>
<p><i>Data source: mobilize.us | Updated: 2026-02-25T07:04:10.471Z</i></p>
