<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Join us to Stand Up for Democracy. Raise your voice for the Constitution, Civil Rights, Due Process, Defunding ICE! Fascism must go! Restore our freedoms and rights. This is a high traffic area with space to gather around Stoughton downtown. 

