        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>BI2 Technologies Protest</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Wednesday, February 25, 2026 at 9:00 PM UTC - 11:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>488 State Rd<br>Plymouth, MA 02360</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Indivisible</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>BI2 Technologies is tracking YOU for ICE. Protest Wednesday, Feb 25, 4-6pm, 488 State Rd, Plymouth (sidewalk in front of office) and every Wednesday, same time. BRING A SIGN &amp; WEAR SUNGLASSES OR GOOGLY EYE GLASSES to make the point - our identities belong to us!

This a local Indivisible event!

Read about BI2&apos;s $4.6 million deal with ICE, and join us to help protect our neighbors and protest this invasion of our privacy.
