        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>Cypress-Tomball Democrats and We Rise Up Protest the Conroe ICE Detention Facility</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Saturday, February 28, 2026 at 4:00 PM UTC - 8:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>1400 N Loop 336 W<br>Conroe, TX 77304</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Harris County Democratic Party</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Cypress-Tomball Democrats are joining with the Montgomery County-based group &quot;We Rise Up&quot; to protest the inhumane Joe Colley ICE Detention Center in Conroe, Tx. 

Detainees are held without full rights (not enough access to attorneys, phone calls out, etc.) and they are in a WINDOWLESS facility with ZERO access to the outdoors 24/7!

More of these facilities are rising up across our country and we need to protest those already here (as well as the new ones!)

Join us as we stand on the pedestrian-friendly Loop 336 and I-45 interchange</p>
