        <name>❌👑 NO KINGS 3 – DENVER 👑❌</name>
        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>❌👑 NO KINGS 3 – DENVER 👑❌</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Saturday, March 28, 2026 at 6:00 PM UTC - 10:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Colorado State Capitol<br>200 E Colfax Ave<br>Denver, CO 80203</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> No Kings</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Denver, we’re back — and this time it’s bigger, louder, and more powerful than ever.

The Denver No Kings 2 saw 46,000–50,000 people flood the West Steps, the lawn, cover Lincoln Veterans Memorial Park, and spill over into Civic Center Park. No Kings 3 is going to be even bigger!

Join us for No Kings 3 – Denver — a bold, unstoppable coalition action bringing together nearly 30 organizations to create the largest and most fired-up Denver No Kings yet! 💥✊

This is what democracy looks like!

No Kings 3 is about standing up to authoritarianism, corporate capture, and empire — including organized resistance to ICE and its ongoing violence against our communities. 🚫🧊

🎤 Rally featuring powerful speakers
🎶 Live music to keep the energy high
🤝 50+ organizations on-site so you can get plugged in, take action, and build community
🔥 A massive march and show of solidarity across movements

📅 Date: March 28
⏰ Time: 12 PM – 4 PM
📍 Location: Colorado State Capitol Grounds

This is more than an event — it’s a movement moment. Together we’re saying loud and clear: No Kings. Not now. Not ever. ❌👑✊

Organized by the Denver No Kings Coalition

Rise up. Bring your friends and a sign. Let’s make history. ✊🔥


*A core principle behind all No Kings events is a commitment to nonviolent action. We expect all participants to seek to de-escalate any potential confrontation with those who disagree with our values and to act lawfully at these events. Weapons of any kind, including those legally permitted, should not be brought to events.*</p>
<p><a href="https://www.mobilize.us/event/903863/" target="_blank">View Event on Mobilize.us</a></p>
<p><i>Data source: mobilize.us | Updated: 2026-02-25T07:04:10.471Z</i></p>
]]></description>
