        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>No Fascists! No Kings!</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Sunday, March 1, 2026 at 6:30 PM UTC - 8:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Northwest Corner<br>West 120th Avenue &amp; Sheridan Boulevard<br>Broomfield, CO 80020</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Indivisible</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Unite together with One Broomfield Indivisible to keep the NO KINGS momentum going! Defend our democracy!

Stand up for your free speech rights and your right to assemble by exercising them with us now!
Don&apos;t let our democracy slip away! Join us every Sunday in Broomfield!

Let&apos;s carry on our fight against the fascist Trump regime and its corporate collaborators like Home Depot, Amazon, and Target!
Let&apos;s pressure the regime into stopping the violence ICE is perpetrating on human beings in our peaceful communities! 
Let&apos;s loudly and frequently oppose the regime&apos;s attempts to rig our upcoming elections NOW and demand equal rights and justice for everyone! 
Demand an end to the erosion of our labor rights even as coroporate collaborators squeeze more and more money out of us for everyday necessities!

Together we will hold them accountable. We know who really has the power in America—and it&apos;s the people!

Bring your favorite sign--choose the topic most important to you!

No Fascists! No Kings!

This is a local Indivisible event by One Broomfield Indivisible(OBI)

Stay safe and stay warm. Dress for the weather and wear a warm hat and appropriate footwear for the conditions. Remember to stay hydrated even in cold weather.

*A core principle behind all Indivisible events is a commitment to nonviolent action. We expect all participants to seek to de-escalate any potential confrontation with those who disagree with our values.*</p>
