<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Authoritarians and “wannabe dictators” like Donald Trump depend on financial support and compliance from the business community. Just look at how many corporations donated to the White House East Wing “renovation” - (https://www.nbcnews.com/politics/white-house/list-donors-trump-new-white-house-ballroom-east-wing-rcna239481).

