<h3>PXP at Students United Against ICE- -VOTER REGISTRATION &amp; ACTIVATION EVENT- EL PASO</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Sunday, March 1, 2026 at 5:45 PM UTC - 8:15 PM</p>
