--------------------------------------------------------------

Our new volunteer group #CoachellaValleyResists is part of the #ResistTrump Campaign. #ResistTrump aims to achieve that via lawful, nonviolent civil resistance. Its values are Collaboration, Integrity, Nonpartisanship, and Professionalism.</p>
