        <name>ICE Out of Everywhere - The Organizing Continues!</name>
        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>ICE Out of Everywhere - The Organizing Continues!</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Saturday, February 28, 2026 at 6:45 PM UTC - 8:15 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Location not specified</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Indivisible</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Join us for an empowering online webinar dedicated to continuing Indivisible&apos;s and 50501&apos;s call to abolish ICE everywhere. We&apos;ll engage in a dynamic discussion on organizing locally, block-by-block, to build community power and challenge systemic injustice. Additionally, we&apos;ll explore the vital electoral work needed for the upcoming primaries and mid-term elections, emphasizing strategies to elect representatives committed to abolition and reform. Building on the momentum from the National Day of Action on January 31, this is a crucial opportunity to connect, strategize, and take action toward a more just and equitable future.

*A core principle behind all Indivisible events is a commitment to nonviolent action. We expect all participants to seek to de-escalate any potential confrontation with those who disagree with our values.*</p>
<p><a href="https://www.mobilize.us/event/895299/" target="_blank">View Event on Mobilize.us</a></p>
<p><i>Data source: mobilize.us | Updated: 2026-02-25T07:04:10.471Z</i></p>
]]></description>
