<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>1475 E Valley Pkwy<br>Escondido, CA 92027</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Indivisible North County San Diego</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>ICE Out of Escondido – Community Rally
