HUNTER MIRANDA, running in the CA-47 Congressional race, will join us at the 4 Corners to explain his position on Justice, Community, Accountability and how to return power to the American people.  He is a progressive attorney, public education advocate, member of the Choctaw Nation of Oklahoma and a challenger of the political establishment.

