        <name>ICE Out of Home Depot - Genesee Ave.</name>
        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>ICE Out of Home Depot - Genesee Ave.</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Saturday, February 28, 2026 at 7:00 PM UTC - 8:30 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>The Home Depot<br>4255 Genesee Ave<br>San Diego, CA 92117</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> National Day Laborer Organizing Network</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Across the country, ICE agents continue to target immigrants in and around Home Depot stores - workers, customers, and surrounding communities. These raids are chaotic, violent, and sometimes deadly.

Through its silence and inaction, Home Depot is allowing its properties to become staging grounds for enforcement activity. Each incident deepens fear and instability in our neighborhoods.  Our nationwide actions showed that people are paying attention - and now we must keep up the pressure.

These atrocities are happening on Home Depot’s watch.  When a corporation allows its spaces to be used in ways that endanger vulnerable communities and does nothing to intervene, silence becomes complicity.

In San Diego, Home Depot refuses to provide laborers with a safe place to seek work, denying them basic dignity and respect.

On Saturday, February 28, we will protest countywide and demand that Home Depot immediately:

PROTECT DAY LABORERS - Ensure the safety and dignity of workers seeking honest employment outside Home Depot stores.

DENOUNCE THE RAIDS - Publicly oppose immigration enforcement raids that target our community.

KEEP HOME DEPOT PROPERTIES SAFE - Stop allowing Home Depot locations to be used for immigration enforcement activity.

A core principle behind all events is a commitment to nonviolent action. We expect all participants to seek to de-escalate any potential confrontation with those who disagree with our values and to act lawfully at these events. Weapons of any kind, including those legally permitted, should not be brought to events</p>
<p><a href="https://www.mobilize.us/event/903016/" target="_blank">View Event on Mobilize.us</a></p>
<p><i>Data source: mobilize.us | Updated: 2026-02-25T07:04:10.471Z</i></p>
]]></description>
