        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>Protest ICE Terror at ICE HQ</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Friday, February 27, 2026 at 5:00 PM UTC - 6:30 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Department of Homeland Security<br>12500 Tukwila International Blvd<br>Tukwila, WA 98168</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Southend Indivisible</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Join Southend Indivisible and our partners Friday morning (and every Friday rain or shine) 9 am - 10:30 am on the sidewalk outside of ICE HQ in Tukwila to demand an end to the kidnappings of our neighbors, separation of families, and terrorizing of our community by DHS/ICE/CBP.

A core tenet of Southend Indivisible is peaceful, non-violent resistance and we will abide by this at all rallies and protests we host or co-host.

