<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Federal Way WA indivisible</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Join Federal Way Indivisible in partnership with the Southend Friends for Peace and Justice every Sunday from noon-1pm, rain or shine. No sign-up needed, but do so if you want emails from us. Bring your own sign or borrow one provided. We&apos;re standing up for peace and democracy, so if you need sign ideas, things like ICE out, voting rights, civil rights, no kings, etc. are all welcome. All non-violent humans and their furry companions welcome! LOCATION: all four corners of the S. 320th and Pacific HWY South intersection. (by the Commons)</p>
