<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Indivisible</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Making Noise in Des Moines - Wednesday, February 11 from 3 to 4:30pm
It&apos;s time to make Noise in Des Moines. It&apos;s time for ICE to go and end the killing. Come join us at Big Catch Plaza and let the people of Des Moines know that our cause is alive and well. Every month Des Moines Indivisible sponsors two Wednesday rallies at Big Catch Plaza in Des Moines. These rallies provide everyone who attends an opportunity to reach out to our community and let them know that our nation is under attack by an administration which at a minimum should be ensuring the health and safety of our great nation. Come join us as we gather together in solidarity against the Trump administration.


This a local Indivisible event!
A core principle behind all Indivisible events is a commitment to nonviolent action. We expect all participants to seek to de-escalate any potential confrontation with those who disagree with our values.*</p>
