<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Join us for this week&apos;s Rally as we challenge Home Depot&apos;s complicity in the fascist brutality of the ICE Raids and broader pattern of unchecked violence, impunity, and attacks on members of our communities. Cypress Park is ground zero, where they are harassing both workers and the day laborer center.
