        <name>✊ALL OF IT  - Weekly Visibility Events — Saturdays Santa Clarita iCA27</name>
        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>✊ALL OF IT  - Weekly Visibility Events — Saturdays Santa Clarita iCA27</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Saturday, February 28, 2026 at 6:30 PM UTC - 9:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>NECESSARY TROUBLE Corner: Good Trouble 2.0<br>24292 Valencia Blvd<br>Santa Clarita, CA 91355</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Indivisible CA27</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>✊ Weekly Saturdays Actions — ALL OF IT. ANY OF.IT... We push back + Solidarity Visibility Brigade.  We are building momentum for *NO KINGS* on *March 28th*.  We are building community.

This Week on Sat FEB. 21st. demanding ICE OUT, IMPEACH, CONVICT, REMOVE... Of all the admin leaders that are failing us.  Honoring A. Pretti, R. Good, Hands Off Venezuela, No ilegal wars, respect internarional law, - RELEASE ALL THE EPSTEIN FILES,  AFFORDABILITY, DEMOCRACY, DUE PROCESS, cuz we ain&apos;t buying the stories either.  ALL OF IT ... 

Indivisible CA27 is mobilizing EVERY SATURDAY [and sometimes SUNDAYS] and on purpose.

We’re joining cities across the country to continue to protest against ICE, in solidarity with MN, Protest Home DEPORT, Spotify, all of them - all of it!  

We stand with the Venezuelan community for a Free Venezuela - with due process and congressional approval for a LEGAL, forceful, decisive stand.  NO ILEGAL WARS!!  A stand against The Tyrant Maduro Regime but not manipulated by the Trump Tyrant Regime either.   

RELEASE ALL THE EPSTEIN FILES, Affordability, Healthcare; All of it. 

We continue in support of the national blackouts and boycotts extending them all thru 2026 — a coordinated action using economic power to push back against corporate and political systems that enable injustice.  Non-Violent pushback works.

Come and protest for all the reasons you may have.  No time to stay silent.

We’ll gather for a non-violent visibility protest to amplify the message locally and demonstrate that Santa Clarita is awake, engaged, and unafraid to show up.

📅 Date: Every Saturday during 2026 and beyond...
⏰ Time: 10:30 AM – 1:00 PM. or 2:00 PM - Check the listings below.
📍 Location: Necessary Trouble Corner

Corner of Valencia Blvd. &amp; McBean Parkway

Signs (or borrow)

Water and comfort essentials

Your voice and your presence

This is a weekly response — showing the power of a community ready to act constantly when needed.

If you cannot attend in person, you can still make an impact by amplifying posts from the national campaign on social media and sharing coverage with your network.

Let’s remind corporations, elected officials, and the community:
our power goes far beyond the ballot — we control where we put our dollars, our attention, and our bodies.

See you at the corner.

A core principle behind all Indivisible and 50501 events is a commitment to nonviolent action. We expect all participants to seek to de-escalate any potential confrontation with those who disagree with our values.


📍 Stay Connected &amp; Take Action

Check us at our website and [Visit us](https://sites.google.com/view/indivisibleca27/home) 

If you would like to Donate, please visit: [Donate](https://my.cheddarup.com/c/indivisible-ca27/items)  


To become part of iCA27 Freedom of Speech Visibility Brigade GROUP, and join us for Banner Making, other visibility events, planning and specific calls to action, please join us in this specific GROUP: [FoSVB](https://www.mobilize.us/indivisibleca27/event/848326/)  


To become a member of Indivisible CA27 and join us in all our activities, please enroll with us here: [Enrollment Form](https://secure.ngpvan.com/si8-e4Peb0O03hk5wAKeRQ2)

As an activity organized by Indivisible CA27, you can reach us at the following:

CA27indivisible@gmail.com 
- Tel/Text: 323.510.6644</p>
<p><a href="https://www.mobilize.us/event/873803/" target="_blank">View Event on Mobilize.us</a></p>
<p><i>Data source: mobilize.us | Updated: 2026-02-25T07:04:10.471Z</i></p>
]]></description>
