        <name>ICE OUT FOR GOOD - Honk &amp; Wave with Indivisible Oregon</name>
        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>ICE OUT FOR GOOD - Honk &amp; Wave with Indivisible Oregon</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Sunday, March 1, 2026 at 8:00 PM UTC - 9:15 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>North Williams Avenue &amp; Northeast Fremont Street<br>Portland, OR 97212</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Swing Left</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>**Grab your rain jacket (our dry streak is over!) and let&apos;s do this!**

Join your neighbors and fellow Portlanders for a family-friendly Honk &amp; Wave event. We stand united against the horrific ICE abuses and the murder of Renee Good and Alex Pretti. And we reject our bully and corrupt grifter-in-chief, his spineless billionaire capitulators, and his MAGA political cronies.

We’re building a local movement and we need YOU! Let’s make democracy visible, energizing and show it’s worth fighting for. When we show up, we inspire others to do the same, because courage is contagious.

🗽 Bring a sign! 🗽Bring your voice! 🗽Bring your friends, kids, and neighbors!

Whether you stay for 15 minutes or the whole time, your presence counts.

🚗 Parking: Along Williams or Fremont, or the adjacent side streets.

Indivisible Oregon is deeply committed to nonviolence as both a principle and a strategy. We strongly believe that peaceful, nonviolent activism offers social movements the most power to effect change.</p>
<p><a href="https://www.mobilize.us/event/848262/" target="_blank">View Event on Mobilize.us</a></p>
