<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Intersection of 110th &amp; Beaverton Hillsdale Hwy, Beaverton, OR  97005<br>10975 SW Beaverton Hillsdale Hwy<br>Beaverton, OR 97005</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Indivisible Washington County</p>
