        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>JOIN Woodburn Hubbard Aurora Indivisible *DAY, TIME, PLACE GIVEN AFTER YOU EMAIL US*</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Wednesday, February 25, 2026 at 11:30 AM UTC - 12:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Woodburn<br>22 ADDRESS PROVIDED LATER<br>Woodburn, OR 97071</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Woodburn Hubbard Aurora Indivisible</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Join our hardworking, dedicated group of local Woodburn and North Marion County folks who are determined to help our communities cope with the onslaught of ICE and all its devastating consequences. We welcome newcomers and are totally open to new and creative ideas. We are a new chapter and really need all hands on deck. We are a warm, friendly group with a tight focus on problem-solving. If you want to learn more about what we do, and where and when we meet, contact us by email WoodburnIndivisible@Yahoo.com and tell us a little about yourself. A real human will do their best to promptly answer your questions and tell you about us. We believe that if you&apos;re not part of the solution, then you&apos;re part of the problem. Come help us create the solutions that Woodburn, Hubbard, Aurora and our region so desperately need to repair the damage the current federal administration has caused.</p>
<p><a href="https://www.mobilize.us/event/896038/" target="_blank">View Event on Mobilize.us</a></p>
