        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>Citrus Heights Resists ICE! Hosted by Sunrise Solidarity</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Saturday, February 28, 2026 at 6:00 PM UTC - 8:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Sunrise Boulevard &amp; Greenback Lane<br>Citrus Heights, CA 95610</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Coalition Against Project 2025</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Join Sunrise Solidarity every Saturday from 10am to 12pm to protest against ICE brutality and the corrupt Trump administration! We stand in solidarity to support our immigrant neighbors. The murders of Keith Porter, Renee Good, Alex Pretti, along with many others will not be forgotten, and we will fight for justice! This is a peaceful/nonviolent protest, so bring the good vibes and an original sign if you can.

Location: Meet at the corner of Greenback Lane and Sunrise Blvd
Time: Every Saturday from 10am to 12pm

Citrus Heights
RALLY
ANTI-TRUMP ANTI-ICE
EVERY SATURDAY 10AM-12PM
MEET AT CORNER OF GREENBACK LANE &amp;
SUNRISE BLVD
SNACKS, DRINKS, SIGNS, &amp; SOLIDARITY AVAILABLE — WE JUST NEED YOU!
Hosted by Sunrise Solidarity</p>
