    <Placemark>
        <name>Camarillo Bridge Brigade - No Ice! No Kings!</name>
        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>Camarillo Bridge Brigade - No Ice! No Kings!</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Saturday, February 28, 2026 at 7:00 PM UTC - 9:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>32 Carmen Dr<br>Camarillo, CA 93010</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> California Democratic Party</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>On Saturday, February 28th, we in Camarillo once again speak out to show our love for democracy and justice!  

Please join the **Democratic Club of Camarillo** and the  **Visibility Brigade** on the Carmen Bridge overpass to decry ICE atrocities and the unceasingly awful Trump regime. 

**We&apos;ll also be out there reminding everyone to attend one of the 2000-plus No Kings actions occurring on 3/28/26 in all 50 states!**

Have your voice heard!! Bring a hand-held sign with a topic of your choice. Big American flags are great too!

You will find ample parking in the Trader Joe&apos;s / Harbor Freight strip mall, just a 800-foot walk to the bridge. (To find us on your map app, use 32 Carmen Drive, Camarillo 93010 to locate the center of the bridge.)

Please RSVP, so we can anticipate the number of attendees for this event. And share this with your like-minded friends!</p>
<p><a href="https://www.mobilize.us/event/909262/" target="_blank">View Event on Mobilize.us</a></p>
