<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Federal immigration enforcement has taken another life. On January 24, Alex Jeffrey Pretti was killed during a federal enforcement action in Minneapolis. This follows multiple recent shootings by federal agents and exposes a dangerous pattern of militarized operations in our communities.

