        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>Making Anti-ICE Whistle Kits</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Saturday, February 28, 2026 at 11:00 PM UTC - 1:00 AM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>757 San Carrizo Way<br>Mountain View, CA 94043</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> It&apos;s Blue Turn</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Join us for a hands-on work session to assemble Anti-ICE Whistle Kits that help our neighbors stay safer and more prepared in the face of immigration enforcement.

Each kit will include a whistle, basic “Know Your Rights” info, hotline numbers, simple guidance for how bystanders can safely support someone being targeted by ICE, and more.

No experience required, just a willingness to help. All materials will be provided; feel free to bring a friend and a dish to share (all our events are potlucks).</p>
