        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>Write Postcards to register purple state people to vote</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Sunday, March 22, 2026 at 10:00 PM UTC - 12:00 AM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>New Parkway Theater<br>474 24th St<br>Oakland, CA 94612</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Swing Left</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Join us at New Parkway Theater to write postcards to remind people in purple states to register to vote for the midterm elections in November. If we want to stop Trump&apos;s economic disaster and the terror of ICE troops, we need to win the midterm elections. That starts now with reminding likely Dems to register to vote. We have a capacity of 15 people for this event.

What Do I Need To Do ? Bring yourself and either 20 postage stamps for postcards or money to purchase stamps, ($15). However no one is turned away for lack of funds. We will provide postcards, pens, scripts and addresses.

Hope to see you there</p>
