        <name>Dump Trump Peaceful Demonstration</name>
        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>Dump Trump Peaceful Demonstration</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Saturday, March 7, 2026 at 9:30 PM UTC - 10:30 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Christie and Powell, Emeryville<br>Christie Avenue &amp; Powell Street<br>Emeryville, CA 94608</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Indivisible</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Every Saturday, 1:30 - 2:30, we rotate to a different corner in Oakland and Emeryville to raise awareness that things are not okay and let our friends and neighbors know that we are fighting for equity, democracy, a clean environment, science-based healthcare, no cuts to those most in need, stopping ICE raids, and more. Please join us!

This a local Indivisible event!

Bring a sign, cowbell, flag, or just yourself! The point is to raise awareness, remind our community that we are paying attention and we vote!


*A core principle behind all Indivisible events is a commitment to nonviolent action. We expect all participants to seek to de-escalate any potential confrontation with those who disagree with our values.*</p>
