<p><strong>When:</strong> Wednesday, March 4, 2026 at 1:00 AM UTC - 3:00 AM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Location not specified</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Oliver Ma for Lieutenant Governor 2026</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Help win real change in California by volunteering with Oliver Ma. Join our weekly phone banks to reach voters and build support for affordable housing, divestment from Israel, and protecting immigrant families.

Oliver is a civil rights lawyer who has taken on slumlords and ICE, and now he&apos;s running for Lieutenant Governor. But he can&apos;t do it alone. We need you.

Join from anywhere. No experience needed. Training provided.</p>
