<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Join us for a Zoom call where we will call New York leadership, Governor Kathy Hochul, Carl Heastie, and Andrea Stewart-Cousins to demand that they pass New York for All Act and the MELT Act. 

Let&apos;s get ICE the hell out of our towns and cities!</p>
