        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>🔥 Students Rise Up Leaders Call 🔥</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Sunday, March 15, 2026 at 11:00 PM UTC - 12:00 AM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Location not specified</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Sunrise Movement</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Right now, our system is captured by billionaires and the politicians they’ve bought. This isn’t new. We’ve watched as college gets more expensive, good jobs disappear, and our futures get more uncertain. Now, Trump&apos;s ICE is kidnapping and killing in our communities. The stakes are high, it&apos;s time to rise up.

We refuse to cooperate with billionaires, the two-party system, and authoritarianism.

Join us to train up on the skills you need to kick ICE off your campus and out of your community &amp; prepare to rise up with students and workers across the country on May Day to bring the authoritarian regime and the billionaires propping it up to their knees. 

Read the guidebook, commit to organizing your school, and see you on the call - smvmt.org/riseup.</p>
